review_content: With this horrendous Covid-19 Virus Crisis I have been ordering 99 percent of my product needs on line, which turned out to actually be a blessing in disguise because of the quick service and ease of ordering. I recently ran out of one of my favorite cereals and when I saw this product (Giant size, 27.2 oz. Honey Nut Cheerios made with real honey) on Amazon for an amazing bargain price I immediately ordered it.I received it the next day after ordering it and I am very pleased with my purchase.  It is fresh and delicious when eating it with a cup of milk.  If you like Cheerios cereal you may want to try the honey nut variation. It has the just amount of sweetness to make it a pleasure to eat.  Check out this product on Amazon for the very best prices.Rating: 5 Stars.  Joseph J. author: meshelle
date_of_review: Reviewed in the United States on March 21, 2021
review_content: Cheerios Honey Nut Cheerios come in at an unbeatable price if you take advantage of the subscribe & save offer which I do. They are full of flavor & definitely fresh. I attached pictures of the nutritional value that are not shown in the description of the Cheerios. The front left corner is deceiving because it claims 140 calories but that‚Äôs if you have 1 cup of just Cheerios alone~no milk. If you chose 1 cup with skim milk it‚Äôs 180 calories. As you can see from my pictures this is loaded with sugar & carbs. This is not the most healthiest breakfast & I assume most people eat more than 1 cup. It does offer a variety of essential vitamins which are needed each day~a positive. All in all it‚Äôs your choice to choose this as your morning breakfast. There are healthier choices out there but if you‚Äôre a Cheerios lover s heads up on what you‚Äôre eating.
title: Cheerios Honey Nut Cherrios
